follow
Discworld player help
follow

Name
.SI 5
follow - Used to follow other monsters or player.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
follow <player/monster>
unfollow <player/monster>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Used to follow a person/monster around as they move from room to room.

Conditions under which it will fail.  You will not keep following someone
you are attacking and it will not follow someone through a teleport.
.EP

See also:
.SI 5
lose.
.EI
